{
  "stem": "12402.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So they-- we loaded up, and my boss asked me, [? no, ?] when are you going to sit?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I said, not yet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, I see this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're chasing them, machine guns, and they were-- they had little cans, they were begging for water.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they knocked the-- the cans out of-- with the machine guns, from both sides, German, chased them and chased them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it took maybe a half an hour till they-- that went through the village, and the Germans watched.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Somebody wanted to help.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They'll knock them out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, the-- whatever they give them, they-- whatever they want to give them, they wouldn't let them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I figured I'm going to follow them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I let them-- I let them go on the highway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They went the same highway I went to the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was ready to go, so I waited a while.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were walking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was travelling.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I followed slowly, slowly, I followed the whole-- the whole group.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one woman-- whoever was behind, it didn't matter, they shot them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't wait.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't wait.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But this woman, she had legs like this-- I'll never forget the site.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I stopped the wagon, and I helped her up to my wagon-- it was a dangerous thing to do, you know, but I didn't care.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I got up to the wagon, and I asked her-- what-- she couldn't walk any longer, her feet couldn't carry her-- so I asked, where are you from?",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
